  # About

  <cite>First Hand</cite> is a publication on process by writers, designers, and media and visual artists in their final year of post-secondary education. It was started by <a href="http://cargocollective.com/campbellcreative">Geoff Campbell</a> and <a href="http://kennethormandy.com">Kenneth Ormandy</a> at Emily Carr University in 2014.

